    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment is judged sufficient for regulatory submission. The majority of assessed factors demonstrate credibility levels consistent with MRL 5 expectations, and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides confidence in hemolysis predictions across the operating envelope. Remaining factor gaps are considered manageable given the conservative hemolysis threshold margin observed in simulation results.",
